  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  LeftSpeaker:
  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 5050be3708712824cb3b9607af44d524, type: 3}
  RightSpeaker:
  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 5050be3708712824cb3b9607af44d524, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: c70a3f94c220d574cb47d187a3da6e95, type: 3}
  text:
  - Hello. I am on the left side!!!
  - Good day. I am on the Right side!!!
  - Now, right is square...
  - left again...
  - This text is really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really really really really really really really really really really really
    really  long...
  - To use the dialogue system, give the thing you want to interact with a "dialouguer"
    and an "Interactable". set the interact distance in the interactable, and set
    the sprites for the speakers, the text, and the meta for the text in the dialouguer!
  - look at the NPC for reference!
  textMetadata:
  - L,0
  - R,0
  - R,1
  - L,0
  - R,0
  - L,0
  - L,0
